title: GTA+
headline: GTA+
subtitle: This Month’s Benefits
content:
In addition to the recurring monthly GTA$500,000 deposited directly into your Maze Bank account, GTA+ Members who've signed up for this month (February 5 - March 4) will also receive:

— The Dewbauchee Champion (Super)
— 50% off Agency Properties and their Upgrades and Modifications
— 2X Rewards on Security Contracts
— The LS Golf Club Varsity
— And more

Membership automatically renews monthly, cancel anytime. Visit rsg.ms/gtaplus for more info.
